title: Bojangles with Jesse Farrar and Mike Hale (LIVE)

description:
Jesse Farrar & Mike Hale join the 'boys to discuss their preferred celestial objects and Nashville eats before a review of Bojangles. Recorded live at Zanies Comedy Club in Nashville on 4/20/22.
